      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783516119196,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "No guessing — describe\nsymptoms, get the cause.\n\nOne-stop service -\nDiagnosis ->Honda parts\ncatalog price -> ordering.\n\nCost & time savings\n(right part first time).\n\nKnow the urgency + what\nhappens if you don't fix\nit\n\nHonda motorcycle\nexpertise built-in. ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "No guessing — describe symptoms, get the cause. \n\nOne-stop service -  Diagnosis ->Honda parts catalog price -> ordering. \n\nCost & time savings (right part first time).\n\nKnow the urgency + what happens if you don't fix it\n\nHonda motorcycle expertise built-in. ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
